# NOTE: the built frontend (hardware_cockpit/public/item_cockpit/ and
# hardware_cockpit/www/item_cockpit.html) IS committed so that a git-based deploy
# (bench get-app + migrate + restart) works without running a Node build on the server.
# Rebuild with `cd frontend && yarn build` and commit the result when the UI changes.

